data.description: Nestled in the family friendly neighborhood of Sinclair, this immaculate 2 story home is an easy commute to Fort Liberty.  The main level features a formal dining area with coffered ceiling, mud room, family room with fireplace and living room. An island with pendant lights, granite counters, tile backsplash, pantry and breakfast area complete the kitchen.  Open the sliding door or look out the kitchen window onto the large backyard and covered deck with dense cedars that provide privacy along the properties edge.  Upstairs has been updated with custom built-ins in the 5th bedroom/bonus room and a modern tiled shower in the owner's suite bath. A large walk-in closet, double sinks and a generous bedroom complete the owner retreat.   The floor plan of this home allows for a natural, relaxed flow between spaces. This property is truly move-in ready.
